==Japanese==
===Etymology===
[[Category:Japanese language|けんき']]
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[元]] || [[気]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
[[元]] (げん, ''gen''), "origin" + [[気]] (き, ''ki'') "spirit"

=== Noun ===
{{janoun|げんき|genki|index=けんき'}}

# [[health]], healthfulness
#* 元気になる
#*:げんきになる
#*:''genki ni naru''
#*:to get well (recover from sickness)
# good spirits
# (personal) energy, enthusiasm
#* 元気を出す
#*:げんきをだす
#*:''genki o dasu''
#*:to cheer up; to recover one's strength

